      "id": "920b257d_9fed7c74",
      "file_path": "cps-ncmp-service/src/main/java/org/onap/cps/ncmp/impl/datajobs/subscription/cmavc/CmAvcEventSingleConsumer.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 45,
      "message": "for the sake of keeping it simple I would remove the SIngle version for now. We can always re-add later if needed. I am sure they way it works with MaxPoll that is if there are no new message for a little whiel it will send whatever it has batch so far even if only one....",
