      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 45,
      "message": "Hi daniel, we are aware of that, Lee Anjella is trying to make a custom annotation that will allow a batch processing but WITHOUT transactions (when EOS feature is disabled)\nBatchsize 1 or small wont make a practical difference (for the consumer) as long as we can turn off teh transactions....",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 6639,
        "name": "Toine Siebelink",
        "display_name": null,
